
LET BE THE NAME OF THE  SIM CHANGE ALERT & PROTECTION SYSTEM (SCAPS) 

1.	Introduction
This proposal is for Business according to Ethiopian business law and regulation. 
2.	 Dashboard module 
•	Dashboard and Interface color should be Green blue and red as needed wide dashboard 
•	The system is both for Android and PC
3.	 Registration  module 
•	Voluntary registration of customers
•	Owner full name
•	Unless payment is confirmed protect registration but not on trial 
•	IMEI 1 and 2  on registration
•	Phone  model
•	SIM number if SIM two registered both
•	Address, city/town, sub-city , district/ wereda/ kebele,house No.  selection option/by dropdown list 
•	Online registration  with payment option online through  telebirr or bank
•	Place for National ID number 
•	Payment  confirmation box
o	Telebirr or bank during registration
o	Payment features is needed to automatically approval
o	Place for telebirr connection  and bank payment options
o	Show amount or payment approved 
o	Payment limitation option 
o	Payment is changeable based on durations are sat by admin- three month, six month  yearly
o	Do not restrict without payment during trial
o	Payment is by  Eth birr   
o	Use for  payment by dropdown list

4.	Security   module 
	Admin and password needed but not during trial
	Prepare place user name and password  	for end users 
	Strong protection from an authorized users /individuals and on line thefts/hackers 
	Password change option
	Do not show total revenue 
	Other related to security  
5.	SIM Change Report Security Alert module 
	Number of SIM that insert to the lost cell phone 
	Show  the theft SIM number inserted to lost phone, the name through  true caller or Ethiotelecom network
	Name of registered customer name, SIM Number address detail.
	Date and  time 
	Reporting system is two ways phone owner and  to the central management of the system (SCAPS)
6.	Deploy Module
•	The system downloadable for use, self-deploy add setting for installation on pc and Android phone
7.	Android Module
•	Design for Android phone communication option or option using both PC cell phones 8. 
8.	Solution Module
•	Solution to open lock phone if the lost phone obtained by tracking
9.	Legal entities Module 
•	Possibility of communicated legal entities
10.	Tracking module
Track the lost cell phone through GPS/ ethiotelecom network
11.	 Back Module
•	Make for all modules back option


